{"word":"ἀμφότεροι","slug":"ἀμφότεροι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἀμφότεροι, αι, α</el></b> [<el>ἄμφω</el> ‘both’]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> of two: <b><i>both</i> <a href='B:490 6:39'>Lk 6:39</a>; <a href='B:560 2:16'>Eph 2:16</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> of more than two (a later usage, with focus on close association within a group): <b><i>all</i> <a href='B:510 19:16'>Ac 19:16</a>; <a href='B:510 23:8'>23:8</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἄμφοδον\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀμώμητος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}